---
title: "applyAllowlistedWorkflowsUpdates (WorkflowRouter)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_empty: check removes and adds
    q_check_empty --> q_error_empty: both empty
    q_error_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList
    q_check_empty --> q_remove_loop: at least one non-empty
    q_remove_loop --> q_remove_targets: for each workflowId to remove
    q_remove_targets --> q_remove_wf: _applyAllowlistedTargetsUpdates(all targets removed)
    q_remove_wf --> q_remove_loop: s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.remove(workflowId)
    q_remove_loop --> q_add_loop: removals done
    q_add_loop --> q_check_zero: for each workflow to add
    q_check_zero --> q_error_zero: workflowId == bytes32(0)
    q_error_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue
    q_check_zero --> q_add_wf: workflowId != bytes32(0)
    q_add_wf --> q_add_targets: s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.add(workflowId)
    q_add_targets --> q_add_loop: _applyAllowlistedTargetsUpdates(targets added)
    q_add_loop --> [*]: all adds processed

    note right of q_remove_targets
        INV-001: Removing a workflowId cascades removal of all targets and selectors
        INV-002: Zero workflowId cannot be added
        INV-003: Caller must have DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
    end note
